---
title: Shrimp Saganaki with Tomato Marinara, Feta and Israeli Couscous
description: Greek food has so much more to offer than just gyros and tzatziki. Introducing bold and flavourful shrimp saganaki! In this dish, tender shrimp are layered with tomato sauce, olives, and tangy feta cheese.
